    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378160/extras/46edb4da5ae64d27fc83ce3a5c9d0cb2.poster.avif?t=1756828045\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378160/extras/46edb4da5ae64d27fc83ce3a5c9d0cb2.webm?t=1756828045\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378160/extras/46edb4da5ae64d27fc83ce3a5c9d0cb2.mp4?t=1756828045\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在这款融合解谜要素的殖民地建造游戏中，你将寻找母舰 AUTARKIS 的遗失部件。你需要同时管理多个定居点，并通过传送门为它们提供支持。但要小心你所造访的星球充满危险。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >策略性的殖民地布局</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378160/extras/d999e4a4a2f0b5e25ed6589474f92839.poster.avif?t=1756828045\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378160/extras/d999e4a4a2f0b5e25ed6589474f92839.webm?t=1756828045\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378160/extras/d999e4a4a2f0b5e25ed6589474f92839.mp4?t=1756828045\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>当定居者在星球上着陆时，他们将面临严酷的环境。每一栋建筑都依赖邻近建筑而运作。你必须深思熟虑，才能打造出最高效的殖民地结构。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >同时管理多个殖民地</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378160/extras/c97f166b1d742dbc964ab2136d7623d6.poster.avif?t=1756828045\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378160/extras/c97f166b1d742dbc964ab2136d7623d6.webm?t=1756828045\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378160/extras/c97f166b1d742dbc964ab2136d7623d6.mp4?t=1756828045\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>先进的传送门技术使你可以同时运营多个殖民地。探索星球的新区域，寻找飞船的遗失部件。然而，有时候你也可能不得不放弃其中一个定居点。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在绝境中生存</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378160/extras/956f86965a52cfab477fc35c552c2bcd.poster.avif?t=1756828045\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378160/extras/956f86965a52cfab477fc35c552c2bcd.webm?t=1756828045\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378160/extras/956f86965a52cfab477fc35c552c2bcd.mp4?t=1756828045\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>外星环境十分恶劣。你的殖民地可能会遭遇陨石雨、有毒云雾、洪水，甚至整个区域的崩塌。在最糟糕的情况下，你将不得不发起新的定居任务。失败，是游戏体验的一部分。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >适应多变的星球环境</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378160/extras/b707e07928f994462e73e3db93e29e9d.poster.avif?t=1756828045\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378160/extras/b707e07928f994462e73e3db93e29e9d.webm?t=1756828045\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378160/extras/b707e07928f994462e73e3db93e29e9d.mp4?t=1756828045\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>你将登上多种类型的星球，每个都有不同的生存挑战。在类地星球、巨型蘑菇林或风沙肆虐的沙漠高原中建立你的定居地。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >踏上重返 AUTARKIS 的旅程</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378160/extras/fcaefb4f411ef4338a6f9628ee6c8cc8.poster.avif?t=1756828045\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378160/extras/fcaefb4f411ef4338a6f9628ee6c8cc8.webm?t=1756828045\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378160/extras/fcaefb4f411ef4338a6f9628ee6c8cc8.mp4?t=1756828045\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>每一次定居任务的终极目标，都是返回母舰 AUTARKIS。最好能带回你所寻找的飞船部件，但定居者的生命始终是你的首要任务。",
